<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/small-business-commissioner> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We ensure fair payment practices for Britain’s 5.5 million small businesses, and support them in resolving their payment disputes with larger businesses. SBC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Business and Trade ."@en .
